data.description:
As you enter through the spacious mudroom, you'll immediately be greeted by an expansive open-concept living space flooded with an abundance of natural light streaming in through a wall of large windows. Follow the soaring cathedral ceilings upwards to discover a second-story bedroom and a generously sized loft area. From this vantage point, you can take in the breathtaking view of the remarkable kitchen, boasting elegant maple cabinets and sleek granite countertops, complete with an oversized island. The kitchen seamlessly flows into a spacious dining area that connects to the living room, making it the perfect setting for family gatherings.

The main level also features a generously sized bathroom with laundry hookups, two separate sinks and vanities, and a double shower head for added convenience. The primary bedroom on this level is adorned with beautiful hardwood floors and offers an entire wall of closets to meet all your storage needs. Completing the main level is another well-appointed bedroom with natural hardwood floors and ample closet space, as well as an additional year-round sunroom that can be utilized to suit your preferences.

Step outside onto the expansive deck, which leads to the fenced-in, level backyard—a perfect outdoor space for your enjoyment.
